HEADWORD: Quadri-
<hw>Quad"ri-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L., from <ets>quattuor</ets> four.
See <er>Four</er>.]</ety> <def>A combining form meaning <xex>four</xex>,
<xex>four times</xex>, <xex>fourfold</xex>; <as>as,
<ex>quadri</ex>capsular, having <xex>four</xex> capsules</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

